印地安人隊在10月1日以3比5輸掉了與老虎隊的第一戰，使得他們和另外兩隊的勝差縮小到一場。也因此人們開始討論三隊打平的可能性<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=K8ALAAAAIBAJ&sjid=k1UDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4224,1666046|title=American League Race May End in Triple Tie|work=Evening Independent|date=1948-10-02|page=7}}</ref>。10月2日，印地安人隊擊敗了老虎隊，確保了至少在龍頭之位打平的情勢，而紅襪隊則是以5比1擊敗了洋基隊，終結了洋基隊爭奪的希望，將龍頭之位鎖定為兩隊之爭<ref>{{cite news|title=BOMBERS BOW, 5–1; Red Sox End Yanks' Flag Chances When Kramer Pitches a 5-Hitter|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=1948-10-03|first=John|last=Drebinger|page=S1}}</ref>。10月3日是賽季最後一天，這天紅襪隊在比賽中勝出而印地安人隊則吞敗，因此兩隊戰績也打平在96勝58敗，從而導致必須在隔天的波士頓進行一場決勝加賽<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1AgNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WmoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4554,166717|title=Redsox, Tribe Finish Tied for Lead|work=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]]|date=1948-10-04|page=18}}</ref>。這場決勝加賽的[[主場優勢|主場優勢]]是透過前一周在芝加哥進行之[[擲硬幣|擲硬幣]]所決定的<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/60545475/coin-flip-held/ |title=Coin Flip Held |agency=[[Associated_Press|AP]] |newspaper=The San Bernardino Sun |page=15 |date=1948-09-25 |accessdate=2020-10-04 |via=newspapers.com}}</ref>。印地安人隊選擇派出菜鳥{{le|傑納·比爾登|Gene Bearden}}作為他們的先發投手，儘管比爾登當時只休息一個月，但教練團因他曾在本季兩度擊敗紅襪隊還是將他派上場；而紅襪隊則是派出{{le|丹尼·加爾豪斯|Denny Galehouse}}先發，而不是本季曾三度從印地安人隊手中拿下勝投的{{le|梅爾·帕涅爾|Mel Parnell}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IT4bAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OE0EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6123,1531260|title=Galehouse and Bearden Named Playoff Pitchers|work=The Pittsburgh Press|date=1948-10-04|page=21}}</ref>。

